Your outfit has been assigned to the ALPHA team! By default your HUD indicators will display red chevrons for ally targets and blue chevrons for enemy targets.

You may change your enemy/ally color selections for Outfit Wars in the Interface section of the Settings menu.
Increases the maximum ammo capacity of the weapon by 72.
A more mobile version of the Vanguard's JGX12, the JGX11 turns the Lightning into a powerful artillery platform. NC use only.
This Light Particle Projection Cannon fires a bolt that can pierce multiple armored targets in a single shot, without the traditional arcing trajectory of most ballistics. NSO use only.
Increases the maximum ammo capacity of the weapon by 56.
Increases the maximum ammo capacity of the weapon by 64.

Your outfit has been assigned to the OMEGA team! By default your HUD indicators will display blue chevrons for ally targets and red chevrons for enemy targets.

You may change your enemy/ally color selections for Outfit Wars in the Interface section of the Settings menu.
The frigid battle island of Nexus is marked by icy corridors and steep elevation changes.
A smaller version of the Prowler's Kingsnake, this dual-barrel cannon releases barrage of armor-piercing shots down range. TR use only.
A more compact version of the Magrider's Perihelion, the L-VXC can charge up to three anti-armor protectiles with a flat trajectory. VS use only.
